---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak in Truffle Mushroom Sauce with creamy mash and pan-fried veg
description: The mash that accompanies the juicy sirloin and garlicky veg in this dish is rich and perfectly creamy. Truffle oil imbues the dish with plenty of flavour.
